name: Pīti
description: Weak rapture only causes piloerection. Short rapture evocates some thunder "from time to time". Going down rapture explodes inside the body, like waves. Exalting rapture "makes the body jump to the sky". Fulfilling rapture seems to be a huge flood of a mountain stream. - Music by Stephen Ramsay (@younggalaxy) and James Paterson. Animation by James Paterson (@presstube)
